          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "usp_ProcessExchange_Code27",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to handle the process of turning off a meter in a utility billing system. It performs several validation checks, updates records in the database to reflect the meter's status change, and logs the transaction. The procedure is part of a larger system that manages meter exchanges and status updates."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
