      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity of this stored procedure is medium. It involves multiple validation checks, conditional logic, and transactional updates across different tables. The use of exception handling and transaction management adds to its complexity, but the logic is straightforward and well-structured."
        }
      ]
